online.common
Class OStack

java.lang.Object
  online.common.OStack

public class OStack
extends java.lang.Object

this is a light weight replacement for Vector. It is not threadsafe, and it has no compatibility problems with java 1.1. Some of it's behavior is not strictly stack like or identical to Vector.

Author:
ddyer

public java.lang.Object remove(int i)
remove the i'th element of the stack. This is done by moving the top element, so the order of items in the stack will change if items are removed from the middle.
